title: (Wed Full Show) Bobby, Eddie & Mike D Are About To Have The NFL Game Of A Lifetime + What Movies Have You Seen Over 50 Times? + Why We do The "Pee Dance?"
itunes:title: (Wed Full Show) Bobby, Eddie & Mike D Are About To Have The NFL Game Of A Lifetime + What Movies Have You Seen Over 50 Times? + Why We do The "Pee Dance?"
description:
Find out why Bobby, Eddie and Mike D are about to have the NFL game of a lifetime soon and why they are worrying so much about what to wear and what questions they want to ask once there.... Then, we go around the room and check in with callers about movies we've seen over 50 times and why we choose to keep rewatching them. Plus, we find out the science behind why we do the 'pee dance.'

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
